[
  "Electrical engineer Rit Thirakomen chairs Bangkok-listed MK Restaurant Group known for its value-for-money 'sukiyaki' restaurants.",
  "The restaurant chain was founded by his late mother-in-law as a small Thai eatery in 1962.",
  "After co-founding a book publishing business in 1974, he took to the restaurant trade in 1987, expanding into sukiyaki with wife Yupin. ",
  "Today, MK has more than 700 restaurants, including Japanese food chain Yayoi."
